&lt;p&gt;Here we have done only one iteration to find best angle. To get better accuracy, we can search over at (2 ± 0.5)°. This process can be repeated until we find a suitable level of accuracy.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>image processing</category><category>ocr</category><category>skew</category><guid>http://www.avilpage.com/2016/11/detect-correct-skew-images-python.html</guid><pubDate>Sat, 12 Nov 2016 12:11:17 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>